# Frontend - MERN Stack User Wallet App
This is the **React.js frontend** for the User Wallet Registration and Login system. It allows users to register or log in using their name and phone number, and then interact with a simple Wallet interface.

# Features
- User Registration & Login (via phone)
- Conditional UI rendering with Wallet component
- Axios API integration with backend
- React Hooks (`useState`, `useEffect`)
- Responsive and clean UI

# Technologies Used
- React.js (with Vite)
- Axios
- JavaScript (ES6)
- CSS

